{"type":"message","id":"2ae49991","parentId":"9ef4b966","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:01:40.079Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:07780d7d-3430-46aa-8819-9030f1c25cb8 Otter: 日程提醒检查] 你是 Otter（私人助理），检查今天的飞书日历和任务：\n1. 获取今日日程\n2. 列出待办事项\n3. 发送今日行程概览给用户\nCurrent time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 07:01 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-19 23:01 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773961300078}}
