{"type":"message","id":"cff777f2","parentId":"5f971886","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:02:00.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The calendar and task APIs need user authorization. The user info came through fine though. I need to inform the user that they need to authorize the calendar and task permissions first. Let me check if there's a way to handle this - maybe I need to trigger the OAuth flow.\n\nActually, looking at the error \"need_user_authorization\", this means the user hasn't authorized the Feishu calendar/task permissions for this app. I should let them know about this and suggest they authorize the permissions.\n\nSince this is a cron job that's supposed to send a summary automatically, but the APIs require user auth, I should just report the issue in the response.","thinkingSignature":"c911e92b1c78d7ff88815e24ad6fd376b0b7ca5b3c561fbbf5c51cd1415aba7e"},{"type":"text","text":"今日行程概览（2026年3月20日，周五）\n\n⚠️ **权限不足，无法获取日程和任务**\n飞书日历和任务功能需要您授权后才能访问。请回复\"授权\"或\"去授权\"，我将帮您完成飞书权限授权流程。\n\n授权完成后，我会自动为您发送今日行程概览 📋"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":962,"output":204,"cacheRead":36992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38158,"cost":{"input":0.00038480000000000003,"output":0.000306,"cacheRead":0.00147968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00217048}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773961312389}}
